        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Just now the wise men and the conjurers were brought in before me that they might read this inscription and make its interpretation known to me, but they could not declare the interpretation of the message."
      },
